h3. Issue Summary

Since Bamboo 7.0 the endpoint GET /rest/api/latest/search/branches does not provide all fields on the output that were provided in earlier versions
h3. Steps to Reproduce
 # Send a GET request similar to this example:
{noformat}
curl --user admin:password -H "Content-Type: application/json" "http://bamboo:8085/rest/api/latest/search/branches?masterPlanKey=PR-PL1
{noformat}

h3. Expected Results

The output of the call is as follows:
{code:xml}
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?><searchResults start-index="0" max-result="1" size="1"><searchResults id="PR-PL10" type="chain_branch"><searchEntity xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:type="planSearchResult" id="PR-PL10"><key>PR-PL10</key><projectName>PR</projectName><planName>PL1</planName><branchName>b1</branchName><description></description><type>chain_branch</type></searchEntity></searchResults></searchResults>
{code}
h3. Actual Results

The output of the call is as follows:
{code:xml}
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?><searchResults start-index="0" max-result="1" size="1"><searchResults id="PR-PL10" type="chain_branch"><searchEntity id="PR-PL10"/></searchResults></searchResults>
{code}
h3. Workaround

There is no workaround
